A 32-year-old Generations actor and radio personality is expected to appear in the Pretoria Magistrate&rsquo;s Court today, after being caught by Tshwane police for allegedly driving under the influence of alcohol. He was spotted driving a Jaguar without exercising due caution during the early hours of Friday morning at the corner of Nelson Mandela Drive and Rissik Street, in Sunnyside. He was then released on bail of R1 000.